  Events















































































  Our downstairs event space is a unique and versatile setting for a wide range of events. Set below our luxury airbnb rental, the open floor plan features high ceilings, original hand painted hardwood floors, and vintage inspired decor. This warm, historic space can accommodate 30-75 guest comfortably, making it ideal for intimate gatherings, celebrations, workshops, and more.If you're looking to host a family gathering, a rehearsal dinner, welcome drink or holiday party, this is a beautiful and unique space just a few minutes from Watkins Glen in the heart of the Finger lakes wine country.

